# Boll Game

## Introduction
Boll is an exciting and fun game where players navigate a ball through various obstacles to reach the goal. The game is designed to test your reflexes and problem-solving skills.

## Features
- Multiple levels with increasing difficulty
- Intuitive controls
- Engaging graphics and sound effects
- Leaderboards to compete with friends

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
    ```sh
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/boll-game.git
    ```
2. Open the project in Unity:
    ```sh
    cd boll-game
    open -a "Unity" .
    ```

## How to Play
- Use the arrow keys or WASD to move the ball.
- Avoid obstacles and reach the goal to advance to the next level.
- Collect power-ups to gain special abilities.

